    7: note("Be able to run and independently check one converged load flow.", "Voltage is an outcome of network impedance, P/Q transfer and controls. A control target is not proof that the target can be achieved within equipment limits.", ["Controllers fighting over the same bus", "Ignoring converter current/P–Q capability", "Checking only one demand/export condition"], "Recommend a voltage-control mode and explain its limits and failure cases."),
